[1] Auth URL from loginAnthropic():

    endpoint:            https://claude.ai/oauth/authorize
    redirect_uri:        http://localhost:53692/callback
    response_type:       code
    code_challenge_method: S256
    state:               QGD_IbtM... (43 chars)
    code_challenge:      XabsnyMc... (43 chars)

[2] HTTP callback → http://localhost:53692/callback

    HTTP 200 - <html>...Anthropic authentication completed. You can close this window.</html>

[3] Aborted after callback proof (expected)

=== 9/9 checks passed ===
  ✓ Authorization endpoint is claude.ai/oauth/authorize
  ✓ redirect_uri derived from callback host (loopback)
  ✓ response_type=code
  ✓ code_challenge_method=S256
  ✓ PKCE challenge present
  ✓ state (CSRF) present
  ✓ Callback server responded HTTP 200
